00:14:26,713 --> 00:14:30,213
君の日々を照らす太陽になりましょ！えへ！
Let me be the sun that shines on your days! Ehe!

114
00:14:30,713 --> 00:14:33,513
Kobokers声上げて！
Kobokers, let me hear you!

115
00:14:38,513 --> 00:14:48,713
3人で･･･ホロライブインドネシア3期生、holoh3roでーす！
The three of us are... hololive Indonesia Gen 3, holoh3ro!

116
00:14:53,513 --> 00:14:59,213
やあ ついにホロライブID5周年ライブができるとはわ
Wow, I can't believe we're finally having a hololive ID 5th anniversary concert.

117
00:14:59,513 --> 00:15:03,213
一曲目からもうめっちゃカッコいいよね！その熱き、感じてるわ！わ！
The first song was already so cool! I can feel the heat!

118
00:15:04,172 --> 00:15:05,472
Satu lagu dari awal udah keren banget kan?
From the very first song, it's already so cool!

119
00:15:05,472 --> 00:15:06,172
Parah sih... iya kan?
That was insane, right?

120
00:15:06,172 --> 00:15:07,672
Adrenalin banget...
The adrenaline is really pumping...

121
00:15:07,672 --> 00:15:09,672
pengen lari aku rasanya nih!
I feel like I want to start running!

122
00:15:10,172 --> 00:15:12,672
Woi woi woi... mau ke mana?
Hey, hey, hey! Where are you going?

123
00:15:15,172 --> 00:15:18,172
Iya iya stop stop stop!
Whoa, whoa, stop, stop, stop!

124
00:15:19,172 --> 00:15:21,172
Nanti keringetan loh, nanti keringetan!
You're gonna get all sweaty!

125
00:15:22,172 --> 00:15:23,172
Kalau Kaela gimana?
How about you, Kaela?

126
00:15:23,172 --> 00:15:27,172
Aduh seru banget... aku enggak nyangka sih
sampai aku bisa ada di sini ya.
Man, it's so much fun... I never thought
I'd actually be standing here.

127
00:15:28,172 --> 00:15:32,172
Tapi ini ngomong-ngomong konser ini masih panjang
banget... jadi kalian tetap semangat ya sampai akhir!
By the way, this concert is still far from over...
so stay hyped until the very end!

128
00:15:33,172 --> 00:15:37,172
Semangat semangat semangat!
Let's give it our all! Give it our all!

129
00:15:38,172 --> 00:15:42,172
Eh tapi ngomongin konser dari tadi...
emang pada tahu judul konsernya apa?
Hey, we've been talking about the concert...
but does everyone know the title of the concert?

130
00:15:43,172 --> 00:15:47,172
Judul konser kita kali ini adalah... Chromatic Future!
The title of our concert this time is...
Chromatic Future!

131
00:15:48,172 --> 00:15:50,172
Ada yang tahu enggak artinya apa? Ayo absen!
Does anyone know what it means? Raise your hands!

132
00:15:51,172 --> 00:15:53,172
Nah ini, Kobo paling tahu!
Now this... Kobo definitely knows!

133
00:15:54,172 --> 00:15:56,672
Iya... yang jelasin yang paling tinggi!
Right... the tallest person should explain it!

134
00:15:56,672 --> 00:16:00,172
Iya, yang jelasin yang paling tinggi! Let's go!
Yeah, the tallest person explains! Let's go!

135
00:16:01,172 --> 00:16:02,672
Gitu ya... ya udahlah...
Oh, that's how it's gonna be? Fine...

136
00:16:03,172 --> 00:16:08,172
Nih ya guys buat kalian yang belum tahu...
Chromatic Future itu artinya masa depan yang berwarna-warni.
Alright guys, for those who don't know...
Chromatic Future means a colorful future.

137
00:16:09,172 --> 00:16:11,672
Jadi karena hololive Indonesia kan udah 5 tahun nih...
Since hololive Indonesia is now reaching
its 5th anniversary...

138
00:16:12,172 --> 00:16:15,172
Kita sama-sama dari hari satu sampai sekarang...
We've all been walking together
from day one until today!

139
00:16:16,172 --> 00:16:23,172
Nah jadi itu untuk ke depannya kita tuh juga harapannya
kita bisa nyiptain waktu dan memori yang berwarna-warni...
So for the future, our hope is that we can continue
to create colorful times and memories...

140
00:16:24,172 --> 00:16:26,672
Sama seluruh fans dari hololive Indonesia!
Together with all the fans of hololive Indonesia!

141
00:16:27,172 --> 00:16:30,172
Betul! Kaela Kovalskia! Catat tuh!
Exactly! Kaela Kovalskia! Take note of that!

142
00:16:31,172 --> 00:16:33,172
Iya iya iya...
Yeah, yeah, yeah...

143
00:16:34,172 --> 00:16:38,172
Nah kalian sekarang udah pada tahu kan...
karena tadi udah dijelasin sama Kaela.
Well, now you all know, right?
Since Kaela just explained it.

144
00:16:39,172 --> 00:16:46,172
Kalau gitu konsernya kan udah mulai nih...
kalian mau nge-post soal konser ini di medsos
jangan lupa hashtag #holoIDChromaticFuture ya!
Since the concert has already started, if you post
on social media, don't forget the hashtag
#holoIDChromaticFuture!

145
00:16:47,172 --> 00:16:51,172
Karena kita pengen banget lihat kalian tuh...
Because we really want to see your...

146
00:16:51,172 --> 00:16:58,172
apa sih... pengen lihat semangat kalian!
how do I put it... we want to see your passion!

147
00:17:00,172 --> 00:17:02,672
Iya itu betul banget! Ya enggak?
Yeah, that's exactly right! Right?

148
00:17:03,172 --> 00:17:04,672
Jangan typo, jangan typo!
Don't make any typos! Don't make any typos!

149
00:17:05,172 --> 00:17:07,672
Asyik! Share ke semua, oke?
Awesome! Share it with everyone, okay?

150
00:17:08,172 --> 00:17:15,172
Jadi... tapi jujur deh kalian tuh pas dibilang
kita bakal konser loh di Indonesia...
kalian pada kaget enggak sih?
But honestly... when you were told that we'd be having
a concert in Indonesia... were you guys surprised?

151
00:17:16,172 --> 00:17:17,672
Halo? Ada yang dengerin?
Hello? Is anyone listening?

152
00:17:18,172 --> 00:17:19,672
Betul!
Right!

153
00:17:20,172 --> 00:17:24,672
Aku setuju juga... aku merasakan empati
terhadap ini adik saya Zeta.
I agree too... I feel a sense of empathy
towards my little sister Zeta.

154
00:17:25,172 --> 00:17:29,672
Empati iya iya...
Empathy, yeah, yeah...

155
00:17:30,172 --> 00:17:31,672
Kalau Kaela gimana, Kaela Kovalskia?
How about you, Kaela Kovalskia?

156
00:17:32,172 --> 00:17:35,672
Aku juga waktu itu enggak nyangka banget
kayak 'Hah? Beneran? Nih riil nih?' gitu kan.
I also couldn't believe it at the time, I was like
'Huh? Seriously? Is this for real?'

157
00:17:36,172 --> 00:17:42,672
Kayak... loh bisa gitu akhirnya mana udah bersembilan
di Indonesia pula ya kan... keren banget!
I mean... finally all nine of us can perform in
Indonesia together... it's so cool!

158
00:17:43,172 --> 00:17:46,672
Keren banget! Iya!
It's so cool! Yeah!

159
00:17:47,172 --> 00:17:50,672
Ini kan konser pertama hololive Indonesia
yang bersembilan.
Yes, this is the very first concert
with all nine members of hololive Indonesia.

160
00:17:51,172 --> 00:17:59,172
Sebenarnya tuh enggak hanya ini tuh momen terbesar
dan terpenting juga untuk fans hololive Indonesia
tapi seluruh dunia juga pasti bakalan nonton enggak sih?
Actually, this is a huge moment for hololive
Indonesia fans, but surely the whole world
will be watching too, right?

161
00:18:00,172 --> 00:18:04,172
Iya enggak?
Right?

162
00:18:05,172 --> 00:18:07,672
Jawab!
Answer me!

163
00:18:08,172 --> 00:18:09,672
Iya iya makasih makasih semuanya!
Yes, yes! Thank you, thank you everyone!

164
00:18:10,172 --> 00:18:15,172
Tapi tentu aja ini pencapaiannya enggak bakal
cuma sampai di sini aja kan?
But of course, this achievement
won't just stop here, right?

165
00:18:16,172 --> 00:18:21,172
Jadi next-nya mungkin kita bisa apa ya...
dominating the world gitu! We are ready!
So next, maybe we can...
dominate the world! We are ready!

166
00:18:22,172 --> 00:18:25,172
Ready ready ready ready!

167
00:18:26,172 --> 00:18:35,172
Betul banget Kaela, Zeta! Selain dari dukungan fans,
kita juga mau mengucapkan terima kasih untuk semua
sponsor yang mendukung terjadinya konser ini!
Exactly, Kaela and Zeta! Besides the support from fans,
we also want to thank all the sponsors
who made this concert possible!

168
00:18:36,172 --> 00:18:43,172
Makasih! Makasih makasih makasih semuanya!
Thank you thank you thank you!
Thank you! Thank you, thank you everyone!
Thank you, thank you, thank you!

169
00:18:44,172 --> 00:18:52,172
Eh tapi ngomong-ngomong di konser ini kayaknya
ada yang beda enggak sih? Hmm... Ela kamu nyadar enggak?
Soalnya kamu paling peka enggak sih?
By the way, doesn't something feel different?
Hmm... Ela, did you notice?
Since you're the most observant, right?

170
00:18:53,172 --> 00:18:57,172
Sadarlah... kalau Kobo mah enggak bakalan sadar.
Nih nih nih nih...
Of course I did... Kobo probably wouldn't notice.
Look at this, look at this...

171
00:18:58,172 --> 00:19:04,172
Yang beda tuh kali ini tuh model kita!
Ini model baru nih!
What's different this time is our models!
These are new models!

172
00:19:05,172 --> 00:19:12,172
Gemes banget! Lucu lucu!
So cute! So cute!

173
00:19:13,172 --> 00:19:20,172
Kameranya dekatin ke aku! Nih nih nih...
kalian mau lihat keimutan Kobo nih nih nih...
Bring the camera closer to me! Look, look...
you want to see Kobo's cuteness, look at this!

174
00:19:21,172 --> 00:19:22,672
Ini nih... o-shiri!
Look at this... my butt!

175
00:19:23,172 --> 00:19:25,672
Eh... oh eh eh eh...
Whoa... whoa, whoa, whoa...

176
00:19:26,172 --> 00:19:31,672
Woi woi woi... ini kamera diambil Kobo semua
enggak sih? Ini ke aku! Aku juga! Aku juga!
Jangan Kobo doang!
Hey, hey... Kobo's taking all the camera time,
isn't she? Point it at me! Me too! Me too!
Not just Kobo!

177
00:19:32,172 --> 00:19:38,172
Satu, dua, tiga... udah selesai!
Kameranya balik ke Kobo lagi!
One, two, three... and done!
Camera back to Kobo again!

178
00:19:39,172 --> 00:19:46,172
Stop stop stop stop stop! Mulai mulai mulai...
semua kamera diambil!
Stop, stop, stop, stop, stop! There she goes again...
taking all the camera time!

179
00:19:47,172 --> 00:19:50,672
Oke oke oke... kalau gitu...
Okay, okay, okay... well then...

180
00:19:51,172 --> 00:19:56,672
Aduh aduh aduh... sampai kehabisan napas.
Jangan berebutan di depan konser!
Man, I'm out of breath.
Don't fight over the camera during the concert!

181
00:19:57,172 --> 00:20:00,672
Iya... iya iya iya...
Okay... yeah, yeah, yeah...

182
00:20:01,172 --> 00:20:04,172
Iya loh... Zeta kalau marah takut loh!
Right... Zeta is scary when she's angry!

183
00:20:03,816 --> 00:20:05,416
Iya deh, kalau Zeta udah ngomong...
Alright, if Zeta has spoken...

184
00:20:05,416 --> 00:20:06,216
Takut ih!
It's scary!

185
00:20:06,216 --> 00:20:08,316
Iya, iya, ya udah deh.
Yes, yes, alright then.

186
00:20:08,316 --> 00:20:11,816
Kalau nggak boleh rebutan kamera sama Zeta...
If I'm not allowed to hog the camera from Zeta...

187
00:20:11,816 --> 00:20:13,816
Hmm... shouganai.
Hmm... it can't be helped.

188
00:20:13,816 --> 00:20:15,516
Kita main aja deh sama Penonton-chan!
Let's just play with the fans!

189
00:20:15,516 --> 00:20:19,316
Kobo pengen deh coba kita teriakin penonton...
I want us to try shouting at the audience...

190
00:20:19,316 --> 00:20:21,316
...karena kan tadi mereka sudah teriakin kita!
...because they were shouting for us earlier!

191
00:20:21,316 --> 00:20:24,316
Maksudnya kita teriakan interaksi kita bareng Penonton-chan-tachi!
I mean, let's do our call-and-response with the fans!

192
00:20:24,316 --> 00:20:26,316
Betul!
Exactly!

193
00:20:26,316 --> 00:20:28,316
Teriaknya bareng penonton, jangan teriakin penontonnya!
Shout with the audience, don't just shout at them!

194
00:20:28,316 --> 00:20:30,316
Iya, gitu maksudnya!
Yeah, that's what I meant!

195
00:20:30,316 --> 00:20:33,816
Soalnya kan habis ini kita harus nyanyi, jadi kita harus simpen suara dulu nggak sih?
Because we have to sing after this, so we should save our voices, right?

196
00:20:33,816 --> 00:20:38,316
Betul ya, nggak bakal selama itu ternyata, tenang aja...
That's right, it won't take that long, don't worry...

197
00:20:38,316 --> 00:20:42,316
...nggak bakal selama durasi stream Kaela gitu ya guys ya!
...it won't be as long as Kaela's streams, okay guys!

198
00:20:42,316 --> 00:20:45,316
Ya udah lah, mau teriak-teriak ya udah, aku nggak masalah dah, aku ngikut.
Whatever, if you want to shout, fine, I don't mind, I'll join in.

199
00:20:45,316 --> 00:20:47,316
Aku ngikut!
I'm in!

200
00:20:47,316 --> 00:20:50,316
Gimana nih semuanya, udah siap belum?
How about it everyone, are you ready?

201
00:20:50,316 --> 00:20:52,316
Siap nggak?!
Are you ready?!

202
00:20:52,316 --> 00:20:55,316
Siap nih kayaknya! Oke, Kobo dulu ya!
Seems like they're ready! Okay, Kobo first!

203
00:20:55,316 --> 00:20:58,316
Aku mau kita sama-sama teriak...
I want us to all shout together...

204
00:20:58,316 --> 00:21:02,316
BOKOBOKOBO!

205
00:21:02,316 --> 00:21:03,816
Oke, siap ya?
Okay, ready?

206
00:21:03,816 --> 00:21:06,816
Satu, dua, tiga!
One, two, three!

207
00:21:06,816 --> 00:21:13,816
BOKOBOKOBO!

208
00:21:13,816 --> 00:21:16,816
Suka, suka! Giliran Zeta, giliran Zeta!
Nice, nice! Zeta's turn, Zeta's turn!

209
00:21:16,816 --> 00:21:19,316
Oke, oke, oke, oke.
Okay, okay, okay, okay.

210
00:21:19,316 --> 00:21:24,316
Pas aku bilang "Mission Statto", kalian bareng-bareng teriak "Start!", ya?
When I say "Mission Statto", you all shout "Start!" together, okay?

211
00:21:24,316 --> 00:21:26,816
Siap? A-a-a... Mission...
Ready? A-a-a... Mission...

212
00:21:26,816 --> 00:21:32,816
START!

213
00:21:32,816 --> 00:21:35,316
Oke, habis ini Kaela!
Okay, next is Kaela!

214
00:21:35,316 --> 00:21:37,316
Oke, oke, oke, oke, nah...
Okay, okay, okay, okay, well...

215
00:21:37,316 --> 00:21:40,816
...buat semua penonton sama Holoh3ro juga...
...to all the audience and Holoh3ro too...

216
00:21:40,816 --> 00:21:46,316
...kalau misalkan aku bilang "Holoh3ro!", kalian bilang "HU-HA!", gampang kan?
...if I say "Holoh3ro!", you say "HU-HA!", easy right?

217
00:21:46,316 --> 00:21:48,816
Langsung, langsung, langsung!
Let's go, let's go, let's go!

218
00:21:48,816 --> 00:21:50,816
Oke ya, siap ya? Holoh3ro!
Okay, ready? Holoh3ro!

219
00:21:50,816 --> 00:21:54,816
HU-HA!

220
00:21:54,816 --> 00:21:59,316
Mantap, mantap, mantap!
Awesome, awesome, awesome!

221
00:21:59,316 --> 00:22:02,816
Keren, keren, keren! Akhirnya Gen 3 kompak juga.
Great, great, great! Finally, Gen 3 is in sync.

222
00:22:02,816 --> 00:22:04,816
Iya, kompak.
Yeah, in sync.

223
00:22:04,816 --> 00:22:07,816
Kelihatannya masih pada semangat nih ya!
Seems like everyone is still full of energy!

224
00:22:07,816 --> 00:22:12,316
Soalnya dari lagu pertama kita hari ini aja udah kerasa banget.
Because even from our first song today, we could really feel it.

225
00:22:12,316 --> 00:22:16,316
Kalian tuh pada nyangka nggak sih kalau lagu pertama kita tuh bakal 100%?
Did you guys expect that our first song would be 100%?

226
00:22:16,316 --> 00:22:20,316
Beh, mana ada yang nyangka. Aku aja sendiri nggak nyangka juga.
Who would've expected it? I didn't even expect it myself.

227
00:22:20,316 --> 00:22:24,816
Langsung dibuka dengan Hoshinova Mode gitu, keren banget kan?
Opening right away with Hoshinova Mode, it was so cool, right?

228
00:22:24,816 --> 00:22:27,816
Keren banget sih! Apalagi tadi Zeta sama nyanyi...
It was really cool! Especially when Zeta sang...

229
00:22:27,816 --> 00:22:31,816
Zeta sama Kaela nyanyi "100%" tuh udah kayak real "100%" ya!
When Zeta and Kaela sang "100%", it was like the real "100%"!

230
00:22:31,816 --> 00:22:37,816
Itu tuh bisa nggak sih... Nggak sekeren tadi, aku tuh jadi ingin kayak...
Is it even possible... It was so cool that it made me want to go like...

231
00:22:37,816 --> 00:22:41,816
Uh, uh! Gitu kan? Kalian pernah nggak sih nyanyi lagu sekeren tadi?
Uh, uh! You know? Have you ever sung a song as cool as that?

232
00:22:41,816 --> 00:22:45,816
Aura farming? Aura farming...

233
00:22:45,816 --> 00:22:51,316
Aura farming sesungguhnya! Keren banget emang lagunya Moona.
Real aura farming! Moona's song really is amazing.

234
00:22:51,316 --> 00:22:56,316
Emang kan Zeta kan soalnya biasanya lagu-lagu yang stylish, yang jazzy-jazzy gitu.
Yeah, because Zeta usually does stylish, jazzy songs.

235
00:22:56,316 --> 00:23:01,816
Jadi tadi pas dinyanyiin tuh ya, "100%", rasanya jadi beda banget vibes-nya.
So when she sang "100%", the vibes felt completely different.

236
00:23:01,816 --> 00:23:04,816
Terus Kaela juga tadi ngerap ya...
And then Kaela was rapping earlier too...

237
00:23:04,816 --> 00:23:09,816
Ta-da-da-da-da-da... Iya, pokoknya keren banget!
Ta-da-da-da-da-da... Yeah, anyway, it was so cool!

238
00:23:09,816 --> 00:23:14,316
Keren banget ya tadi!
It was really cool earlier!

239
00:23:14,316 --> 00:23:19,316
Tapi habis ini tuh masih ada lagi... "NEW zomBIE!" tadi.
But after this, there's even more... That was "NEW zomBIE!".

240
00:23:19,316 --> 00:23:22,316
Ayo, pada tahu dong ini lagu siapa?
Come on, you all know whose song this is, right?

241
00:23:22,316 --> 00:23:26,316
Taulah, taulah, senpai kita, senpai kita.
Of course, of course, it's our senior's song.

242
00:23:26,316 --> 00:23:31,816
Tadi tuh itu ya, Holoro tuh perform-nya juga keren banget, kayak lagi di game gitu.
Earlier, Holoro's performance was also really cool, like being in a game.

243
00:23:31,816 --> 00:23:35,816
Betul, setuju! Terus tadi ada backdancer-nya, men!
True, I agree! And there were back-dancers, man!

244
00:23:35,816 --> 00:23:38,816
Keren ya guys! Keren nggak?!
It was cool, right guys?! Wasn't it cool?!

245
00:23:38,816 --> 00:23:43,816
Terus ada apa lagi tuh tadi? Lampu laser, terus ada efek kembang api segala...
And what else was there? Laser lights, and then fireworks effects and all...

246
00:23:43,816 --> 00:23:47,816
...banyak lah ya gimik-gimik yang "wow".
...there were so many "wow" gimmicks.

247
00:23:47,816 --> 00:23:51,316
Itu backdancer nanti aku hire semua ya buat solo konser aku.
I'm going to hire all those back-dancers for my solo concert.

248
00:23:51,316 --> 00:23:53,816
Wah, udah ngomong konser solo aja.
Whoa, talking about a solo concert already.

249
00:23:53,816 --> 00:23:57,816
Ngomongan adalah doa ya. Tapi konser yang ini belum selesai.
Words are prayers, you know. But this concert isn't over yet.

250
00:23:57,816 --> 00:24:03,816
Belum, belum, belum!
Not yet, not yet, not yet!

251
00:24:03,816 --> 00:24:11,316
Eh, tapi... kalian tahu nggak sih sebelum ini tuh nyanyinya lagu apa?
Eh, but... do you guys know what song was sung before this?

252
00:24:11,316 --> 00:24:16,316
Eh, aku mah tahu banget lah! Itu lagu terbaru aku... "Dahlah".
Eh, I definitely know! That's my newest song... "Dahlah".

253
00:24:16,316 --> 00:24:22,316
Iya, dahlah, nggak usah dibahas.
Yeah, forget it, let's not talk about it.

254
00:24:22,316 --> 00:24:27,816
Lho, kok gitu? Itu tuh maksudnya judulnya "Dahlah", lagunya judulnya "Dahlah"!
Hey, why like that? I mean the title is "Dahlah", the song's title is "Dahlah"!

255
00:24:27,816 --> 00:24:31,816
Oh...

256
00:24:31,816 --> 00:24:36,816
Oh, "Dahlah"! Bilang dong!
Oh, "Dahlah"! You should've said so!

257
00:24:36,816 --> 00:24:41,816
Habisnya kamu kan sering "dahlah, dahlah" gitu, jadi kirain emang beneran "dahlah".
Because you say "dahlah, dahlah" so often, I thought you really meant it.

258
00:24:41,816 --> 00:24:46,816
Entar dahlah-dahlah pulang dia.
Otherwise, she might just say "dahlah" and go home.

259
00:24:46,816 --> 00:24:49,316
Kalau gitu "Dahlah" tuh maksudnya apa sih?
In that case, what does "Dahlah" actually mean?

260
00:24:49,316 --> 00:24:53,316
"Dahlah" sama kehidupan. Hidup tuh berat ya guys ya...
"Dahlah" towards life. Life is tough, you know guys...

261
00:24:53,316 --> 00:24:57,316
...kalau hidup berat ya udah "dahlah" aja, habis itu lanjutkan hidupmu!
...if life is tough, just say "dahlah", and then move on with your life!

262
00:24:57,316 --> 00:25:01,816
Iya betul teman-teman, di kehidupan yang dewasa ini ya.
That's right everyone, in this adult life of ours.

263
00:25:01,487 --> 00:25:06,887
Untungnya lagunya santai, easy listening, jadi kita sambil keliling-keliling kan nyapa fans, gitu ya?
Fortunately, the song is chill and easy listening, so we can walk around and greet the fans, right?

264
00:25:06,887 --> 00:25:11,387
Asyik banget ya tadi ya? Aku juga suka banget tadi dance bagian reff-nya ya?
It was so much fun! I also really liked the dance during the chorus!

265
00:25:11,887 --> 00:25:14,387
Dala dala dala da...

266
00:25:14,387 --> 00:25:16,387
Itu... itu beda lagu gak?
Wait... is that a different song?

267
00:25:17,887 --> 00:25:20,387
Gak gitu deh... kayaknya...
I don't think it was like that... probably...

268
00:25:20,887 --> 00:25:27,387
Ya tapi pokoknya asyik lah ya kalau nyanyi lagu chill santai-santai kayak gini.
Anyway, it's fun to sing chill, relaxing songs like this.

269
00:25:27,887 --> 00:25:29,887
Iya santai dong. Tapi...
Yeah, it's relaxing. But...

270
00:25:30,887 --> 00:25:34,387
...ngomongin soal santai, kita tuh sebenarnya belum bisa santai dulu. Hei, santai!
...speaking of relaxing, we actually can't relax just yet. Hey, chill!

271
00:25:34,887 --> 00:25:36,387
Karena kayaknya katanya gak boleh santai...
Because apparently we're not allowed to relax...

272
00:25:36,887 --> 00:25:39,087
Iya! Iya! Rileks!
Yeah! Yeah! Relax!

273
00:25:39,087 --> 00:25:42,387
Iya iya iya, jangan santai-santai. Jangan terlalu santai.
Yeah, yeah, don't get too relaxed. Don't be too chill.

274
00:25:42,387 --> 00:25:45,887
Karena konsernya tuh masih panjang!
Because the concert is still long!

275
00:25:46,887 --> 00:25:50,887
Jadi sebelum itu, kalian ada gak yang mau kalian sampaiin dulu?
So before that, is there anything you guys want to say first?

276
00:25:50,887 --> 00:25:53,887
Mulai dari ini nih, yang gak bisa diem.
Let's start with this one, who can't stay still.

277
00:25:56,887 --> 00:26:00,887
Tiga kata saja. I love you.
Just three words. I love you.

278
00:26:01,387 --> 00:26:04,887
Keren! The best! Sangat jelas ya.
Cool! The best! Very clear.

279
00:26:05,387 --> 00:26:09,387
Tetap semangat, tetap semangat menjalani hidup ya. Udah gitu aja.
Stay spirited, keep the spirit in living your life. That's all.

280
00:26:09,387 --> 00:26:13,887
Pokoknya sampai akhir masih panjang. Semangat!
Anyway, it's still a long way to the end. Keep it up!

281
00:26:14,887 --> 00:26:18,387
Saranghaeyo! Gomawoyo!
I love you! Thank you!

282
00:26:18,887 --> 00:26:21,887
Oke kalau aku... ya, semangat selalu!
Okay, as for me... yeah, always stay spirited!

283
00:26:21,887 --> 00:26:26,387
Semangat santai! Hidup jangan terlalu dibawa serius.
Chill spirit! Don't take life too seriously.

284
00:26:27,387 --> 00:26:29,887
Semangat santai ya?
A chill spirit, huh?

285
00:26:29,887 --> 00:26:31,887
Semangat santai!
Chill spirit!

286
00:26:33,887 --> 00:26:36,387
Oke kalau gitu kita lanjutkan...
Okay then, let's continue...

287
00:26:37,387 --> 00:26:39,887
Wait wait wait, tunggu dulu!
Wait, wait, wait, hold on!

288
00:26:39,887 --> 00:26:44,887
Sebelum selesai-selesai ini nih ya, kita teriak bareng-bareng penonton dulu gak sih?
Before we wrap this up, why don't we shout together with the audience?

289
00:26:45,887 --> 00:26:49,387
Iya dong! Ayo! Ayo ayo ayo!
Of course! Let's go! Come on!

290
00:26:49,887 --> 00:26:53,387
Oke oke. Jadi kita teriak bareng ya, dalam hitungan tiga.
Okay, okay. So we'll shout together on the count of three.

291
00:26:53,387 --> 00:26:57,887
Kita sama-sama teriak Chromatic Future. Oke ya?
We'll all shout "Chromatic Future" together. Okay?

292
00:26:57,887 --> 00:27:00,887
Oke oke, Chromatic Future! Gitu kan ya?
Okay, okay, Chromatic Future! Like that, right?

293
00:27:00,887 --> 00:27:02,887
Iya iya kayak gitu, kayak gitu.
Yeah, yeah, just like that.

294
00:27:03,387 --> 00:27:06,887
Oke langsung ya, sambil lihat sini sini sini... sambil lihat...
Okay, let's do it, while looking here, here, here...

295
00:27:06,887 --> 00:27:08,887
Aku ya, aku, aku yang penonton ini nih...
Me, me, I'll take this audience...

296
00:27:08,887 --> 00:27:11,887
Iya iya, kalau gitu yang ini center ya...
Okay, then this one will be the center...

297
00:27:11,887 --> 00:27:13,387
Yapoo~

298
00:27:13,887 --> 00:27:16,387
Oke bareng-bareng ya. Satu, dua, tiga!
Okay, together now. One, two, three!

299
00:27:16,387 --> 00:27:22,887
CHROMATIC FUTURE!

300
00:28:01,087 --> 00:28:02,887
Everything was easy

301
00:28:02,887 --> 00:28:04,887
I did it all alone

302
00:28:05,087 --> 00:28:06,687
So effortlessly

303
00:28:06,887 --> 00:28:10,387
I spread my wings and let my magic unfold

304
00:28:10,387 --> 00:28:12,087
Got all problems solved

305
00:28:12,087 --> 00:28:14,087
Without any setbacks

306
00:28:14,087 --> 00:28:16,387
There is nothing uncontrolled

307
00:28:17,087 --> 00:28:19,387
There is no way I can begin

308
00:28:19,387 --> 00:28:21,387
Dream life that I need to win

309
00:28:21,387 --> 00:28:24,687
I need to feel how all these things crumble into little pieces

310
00:28:24,687 --> 00:28:28,387
I know, I gotta soar a little higher

311
00:28:28,387 --> 00:28:31,887
Hope all turns to be the things I desire

312
00:28:32,087 --> 00:28:35,387
Layaknya burung merak yang bersayap
Like a winged peacock

313
00:28:35,387 --> 00:28:37,087
Kan ku taklukkan gelap
I will conquer the darkness

314
00:28:37,087 --> 00:28:39,087
Dengan sihir angin kan ku ajak
With the magic of wind I will invite

315
00:28:39,087 --> 00:28:42,087
Semua yang terlelap tuk bangkit
All those who slumber to rise up

316
00:28:42,087 --> 00:28:43,887
Melawan dunia
Against the world

317
00:28:43,887 --> 00:28:45,687
We'll never give up

318
00:28:45,687 --> 00:28:48,887
As long as we got the strength in ourselves

319
00:28:48,887 --> 00:28:52,387
We could rise above the pain

320
00:28:52,387 --> 00:28:54,087
With hunger and love

321
00:28:54,087 --> 00:28:56,087
Walking step by step

322
00:28:56,087 --> 00:28:58,087
Trusting my own pace

323
00:28:58,087 --> 00:29:01,087
Giving me what I deserve to have

324
00:29:01,087 --> 00:29:02,887
Let's go, just believe me

325
00:29:02,887 --> 00:29:04,387
